{
  "chapter": 43,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十三回 摩伽密宗\n\n本章讲述了辛捷和吴凌风在大戢岛后岛的对话，两人互吐心事，谈得很是融洽。平凡上人向他们讲述了恒河三佛的来历——他们原是天竺摩伽密宗弟子，因野心勃勃而改变教规，广收弟子，独霸天竺，还想扩展势力于中原。平凡上人还讲述了秘笈的来历，原来是达摩秘笈中的轻功篇，被恒河三佛据为己有。平凡上人将轻功要诀传授给两人。\n\n随后，辛捷和吴凌风前往崆峒找厉鹗讨回宝剑，在青元观投下拜柬。于一飞和诸葛明发现拜柬后大惊，决定报告正在闭关修炼上清气功的厉鹗。同时，武当山赤阳道长也收到了同样的拜柬，内心充满恐惧和后悔。\n\n最后，辛捷和吴凌风来到沙龙坪拜访梅山民，向他讲述了别后的经历，包括小戢岛上华夷之争和恒河三佛的武功特点。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "古人都说北山南水，想不到在这江南海外孤岛，竟有如此宏伟景色，天下之大，真是无奇不有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "大江东去浪淘尽，千古风流人物……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "吴大哥，咱们先去把厉鹗那般贼子宰了，再去找阿兰和张菁。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥，我上次被恒河三佛掌伤，我自己用内功疗伤时，我一直苦思一个问题，现在我可想通了，一个人在世上，如果只是徒然武艺高强只是使人人怕你，那有什么意思？要人人都敬重你、心服你，才是真正的英雄豪杰。从今以后，我可要向这方面努力，只是我天性太偏，大哥，你可要好好指导我，教训我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "捷弟，恭喜你，你又进了一步啦，云爷爷说过，要练成绝世武功，不但要天资敏悟，而且要胸怀宽阔，能够包罗万象，你的天资是没有话说的，现在你能悟到善恶是非，不再随性而为，有仇必报，那胸襟自会开朗，海阔天空，日后的成就，真是不可限量哩！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥，能使你这种绝世美男子如此深情的姑娘，只怕是天香国色呢！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "捷弟你别取笑，我曾见过的女孩子，论美，自然要推张菁第一啦。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "捷弟，张姑娘是个很善良的女孩子，你可要一心一意爱她、保护她。哦！对了，上次你被关中九豪重伤时，口口声声喊一个姓方的和一个姓金的姑娘，她们可都是谁呀？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "原来你是为了方姑娘，这才挺身受恒河三佛一掌，你这样为她舍生挡敌，总算报答了她一番深情，她现在已有归宿，那很好，只是金姑娘……好在张菁心地善良，总有解决的办法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥说得是，我常常想，众生芸芸，可是就有那样巧，从千百个人中，你就只会爱上她一个，那么你为她牺牲，为她拼命，很当然的事了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "我们一起去看看平凡上人去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "对了，对了，这几手倒真妙。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "两个娃儿，咱们来赛赛足力，你们两个全力向前跑，看我老人家表演一手给你们瞧。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "您老人家这手真帅，这是那秘笈所载吧！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "娃儿，天下轻身工夫，你道哪种身法最为神妙？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "依晚辈想，如果要算身法神奇难以捉摸，要推小戢岛慧大师的'诘摩步法'。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "我老人家也是这么想，可是你上次看我们'世外三仙'大战'恒河三佛'，你可瞧出什么异样来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "晚辈觉得那三人轻功之快，真有如鬼魅，要论速度，比起慧大师的'诘摩步法'，恐怕尚高一筹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "娃儿，真聪明，我老人家当天等'恒河三佛'走后，苦思他们身法，只觉与中土各门各派大不相同，想了半天，也想不出什么道理来，刚才一看此书，这才恍然大悟。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "这本书上记载的，可就是恒河三佛那一门的轻功吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "你也不笨，来，来，我讲个故事给你们听。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "恒河三佛这一派原是天竺摩伽密宗，教中弟子一生苦修，精研佛理、武功，是以代代都出了不少神能通天的得道高僧，但是教长大位传到这恒河三佛手中，这三人雄才大略，怎肯潜身苦修？是以改变教规，广收弟子，不但独霸天竺，竟想扩展势力于中原。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "只怕没有这么简便。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "恒河三佛一共收了六个徒弟，其中最小的就是上次在无为厅耀武扬威的金鲁厄了。这六个人中，第四个是个苦行僧，名叫巴鲁斯，他因看不惯师父倒行逆施，手段狠辣，便常常进劝忠言，但他师父们不但不听，反而对他厌恶起来，厉害的武艺也不教他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "后来，有一次，一个天竺人拿着祖传的秘笈投奔恒河三佛，教他练书上武功，而恒河三佛也可以照书练习，这人对于武学，可说是完全不懂，他知自己这本祖传秘笈，的确载有一种至高功夫，他访问了许多武师，没有一个人懂得书上的功夫，最后听说恒河三佛武功是全天竺第一，便想出这个交换的方法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "那就是我大哥这本秘笈了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "正是这本，这小册原是达摩秘笈中的轻功篇，恒河三佛一见，自然是大喜过望，但他们怎能容许天竺境内再出高手？是以不但不教那人功夫，反而暗暗把那人害了，这本秘笈便被他们三人据为已有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "恒河三佛武功虽然高强无比，想不到人品却如此卑下，哼，下次再撞着他们，好歹也要见个死活。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "这事被他们第四个弟子知道了，他冒死阻止无效，知道师父对自己已存疑心，本人又不愿同流合污，想了半天，只有逃走一条路。但他一想，三个师父现在武功已是难逢敌手，将来练成经上功夫，岂不是如虎添翼，任他为恶，无人能制了吗？于是偷偷乘大家都不注意，偷了秘笈逃去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "这人品格甚是高尚，他为了表示自己盗书并非是想偷学，而是防止他师父异日武功太高，肆意为恶，是以立誓终身不看书中所载。他在中土数十年，恒河三佛因为羽毛未丰，是以并未到中原追捕他。娃儿，他怎么把这本书交给你云祖师叔，你一定知道的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "云祖师叔有一次遇到他被几个人围攻，出手救了他，但他已身受重伤，自知必死，是以把这秘笈送给祖师叔。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "这书上所载的确是非同小可，那恒河三佛只学会了一半，是以身法轻盈有余，却嫌不够凝重。后半部所载是要有极上乘的内功才能练习，所以就是那苦行僧不偷去，恒河三佛当年也不能练。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "您老人家刚才那手凌空虚渡，可是这书后半部所记载的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "您老人家刚才那手凌空虚渡，可是这书后半部所记载的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "娃儿，—上次恒河三佛没有讨到便宜回去，他们心怀叵测，虽然他们本人不会再贸然入中原，但是他们那个小徒儿金鲁厄上次在大庭广众中栽在辛捷这娃儿手里，迟早要报仇。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "娃儿，你把老尼婆传给你的诘摩步法施一遍瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "这'诘摩步法'你就是不施，我老人家也知道它的好处，临敌之际果真妙入毫厘，所以这就奇怪啦——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "奇怪什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "这天竺轻功如论快捷确是世上无双，诘摩步法也不是对手，但是恒河三佛似乎没有学全，临敌毫无精微变化，但是以恒河三佛的功力，临敌之际也不知变化，难道他们学了这套轻功，只是为快而已吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "如果我老眼不花，这天竺轻功必然还有一桩奇特功用，日后你们若再碰上恒河三佛，就知我言不虚了——好啦，既然这书是你们的，我就把这轻功要诀教你们吧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "要走就走，我老人家可不稀罕。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_feng",
      "speaker_name": "清风",
      "listener": "char_ming_yue",
      "text": "看看天色，不出正午又有一场大雪，咱们是白费心力了——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue",
      "speaker_name": "明月",
      "listener": "char_qing_feng",
      "text": "既是如此，何必还要打扫——",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_feng",
      "speaker_name": "清风",
      "listener": "char_ming_yue",
      "text": "说是如此，我也不想扫了，来，明月弟，好久没有练习过招了，听说日前诸葛叔叔指点了你那套'追云拳'——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue",
      "speaker_name": "明月",
      "listener": "char_qing_feng",
      "text": "对啦，对啦，追云拳……咦……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue",
      "speaker_name": "明月",
      "listener": "char_qing_feng",
      "text": "哥哥，你看是谁到咱们观来投柬帖子——",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue",
      "speaker_name": "明月",
      "listener": "char_qing_feng",
      "text": "哥哥，是什么玩意？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_feng",
      "speaker_name": "清风",
      "listener": "char_ming_yue",
      "text": "果然是一纸拜柬，人家密密封起，我们还是不拆为妙，去找诸葛叔叔他们去看看，他们也许知道——",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_qing_feng",
      "text": "清风、明月，一大早就吵吵闹闹，怎么地没有扫好就偷懒想溜么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_feng",
      "speaker_name": "清风",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "于叔叔，快来看——",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_qing_feng",
      "text": "看什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_qing_feng",
      "text": "清风，这玩意儿是在什么地方拾到的？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue",
      "speaker_name": "明月",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "这个是在观门大匾上拾到的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_qing_feng",
      "text": "你们再去打扫吧——",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ge_ming",
      "text": "大师兄，大师兄……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ge_ming",
      "text": "辛捷，辛捷这厮终于找上门来了——",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ge_ming",
      "speaker_name": "诸葛明",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "这吴凌风既是吴诏云之子，和师尊有不共戴天之仇，看来这件事非得让师尊自己去斟酌了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ge_ming",
      "text": "师父半月来闭关，不知会不会责怪咱们去打扰——",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ge_ming",
      "speaker_name": "诸葛明",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "不，这事情太重要——",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "捷儿——",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "text": "梅叔叔……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "text": "梅叔叔……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "快起来，捷儿，这位一定便是吴贤侄吧。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "哈哈，故人子嗣无恙，又是如此人才出众，吴贤弟英贤有知，也堪告慰九泉了。你们想来还没有吃过早饭吧？别再待在风雪中了，快快进屋里来……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你们此行从何而来？看样子好像奔波不少时候，以老朽看来，至少也赶了四五百里路程！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "text": "咱们正是由武当山赶来的呢——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    }
